(2, 'Industry Global', 1, 'For Mainpage - Industry Global', '2', '<p>Your main goal should be to make sure that your Finance Industry, is easier to navigate and more attractive from your biggest competitors. We believe that you are ready to get services for your industry, Dimarz can help you on your most demanding services such as Website Design &amp; Development, Digital Marketing, Graphics Designing, Data Entry and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a tech team, DiMarz strives to deliver the quality that will help our clients expand their ventures. With our VPO strategy, which stands for Visualize, Process and Outcome we can give your project the best possible results. We visualize and understand the needs our clients want to achieve. Then we process that visualization to bring out the best possible outcome.</p>', '2022-12-15 11:03:14', '2022-12-20 06:29:06'),
(3, 'Search Engine Optimization', 0, 'For Mainpage - Search Engine Optimization', '5', '<h2>We Provide International SEO Services with Smart &amp; Healthy Approaches</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ranking is the first priority of Search Engine Optimization but it should maintain the search engine policies and regulations too. So, we will plan a SEO strategy which will ensure a healthy and long-lasting ranking for your keywords &amp; pages on search engine result pages (SERP).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ranking is not enough! You must track your rankings to know how your keywords and pages are performing on search engines. As an international SEO services provider, we will ensure that your keywords, pages and websites rank, perform well and climb the top of SERP.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Stay Ahead in Competition with DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The key to success in SEO is to beat your competitors to rank on the first page of search engines. But it is not as easy as it seems. A good SEO campaign takes a lot of intensive research, years of experience and a dedicated team to get it done right.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an international SEO services provider, our team is improvised with the latest trends and policies of SEO. We will analyze every bit of your competitors&rsquo; strategies to create a SEO campaign plan to outsmart them. Then we will work throguh your websites technical, on-page and off-page related matters to make it&nbsp;better. This way you will stay one step ahead from your competitors in the top SERP positions and build your way to a better ranking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-12-19 06:45:21', '2022-12-23 10:17:11'),
(4, 'Email Marketing', 0, 'For Mainpage - Email Marketing', '3', '<h2>We Will Be Your Professional Email Marketing Coordinator</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ldquo;A majority of marketers using email leverage mobile-friendly emails as part of their marketing strategy.&rdquo;</strong><br />\r\nEmail marketing plays a vital role in the Digital Marketing sector as it is a direct ticket to advertise your product to potential customers. A well organized campaign can bring greater revenue, higher ROI and more engagement to your brand. Our experienced Email Marketing Coordinators &nbsp;will oversee your campaign to achieve better results.&nbsp;A successful &nbsp;email marketing campaign depends on a variety factor.So you should familiarize yourself with the email marketing coordinator&#39;s role in marketing campaigns.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Minimal Bounce Rate &amp; Decent Engagement</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The percentage of email addresses on your contact or subscriber list who didn&#39;t receive your message because a recipient mail server returned it is referred to as the bounce rate.Sothe first thing that everybody hates about email marketing is the heavy bounce rates which leads people to take it as a waste of money. But, it&#39;s totally different with DiMarz. We value your time and money. Our email marketing coordinators will ensure you an effective campaign which will bring decent brand engagement along with minimal bounce rate. With the latest technologies and research, we are committed to provide you with a better result.</p>', '2022-12-19 10:07:39', '2022-12-23 10:06:57'),
(5, 'WordPress Development', 0, 'For Mainpage - WordPress Development', '2', '<h1>WordPress Development Services That Bring Results</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>WordPress is one of the world&#39;s most popular content management systems. It&#39;s simple to use, versatile, and a template, which makes it an excellent platform for creating websites and blogs. WordPress development services can help you take your website to the next level. Our team of experienced developers can create custom themes, modifications, and enhancements to make your WordPress site faster, easier to use, and more efficient. We know that only some people are familiar with WordPress, so we also offer comprehensive services to build a successful WordPress site.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Key Benefits Of WordPress Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>WordPress Development offers businesses a wide range of benefits:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>It is an incredibly user-friendly platform that allows businesses to create high-quality websites and content easily.</li>\r\n	<li>It offers a vast selection of plugins and themes, allowing businesses to choose their website&#39;s features and design.</li>\r\n	<li>WordPress offers excellent scalability; with a few simple clicks, businesses can upgrade their website and add more features.</li>\r\n	<li>The platform is highly secure and comes with regular updates and maintenance to ensure the highest level of safety for websites.</li>\r\n	<li>WordPress is highly cost-effective, making it attractive to businesses of all sizes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;All these features make WordPress Development an attractive choice for businesses looking to create an effective website.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '2022-12-19 13:41:31', '2022-12-20 06:44:59'),
(6, 'Content Writing', 0, 'For Mainpage - Content Writing', '5', '<h2>Unique &amp; Creative Content Writing Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to content writing, you cannot simply resort to any average person. You need an exceptional professional writer who understands your needs and can come up with unique and interesting ideas for you. This is where our creative content writing services come in. We have a team of professional writers who are not only talented but also have the necessary skills and experience to write well-crafted content. Our writers are dedicated, creative and understand what our clients want. We always try our best to provide the optimal writing services possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>We Provide All Kinds of Contents on Demand</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our team of experienced writers can help you create custom content that is both informative and engaging. We can help you with everything from blog posts and website copy to engaging social media captions or content. We&#39;ll make sure your content is optimized for the search engines and also free of any kind of plagiarism or error. We have a dedicated team who always proofread the writings to ensure its quality. We know the importance of good contents and&nbsp;always strive to research, work and deliver the best content to you. We can assure you that from us, you will get out of the box contents which are sure to fulfill your needs. So, in any case you need some good content for your website, you can count on us.</p>', '2022-12-20 06:32:38', '2022-12-23 10:00:54'),
(7, 'Online Data Entry', 0, 'For Mainpage - Online Data Entry', '2', '<h2>Professional Online Data Entry Services By DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DiMarz offers professional online data entry services to help businesses save time and money. Our team has the expertise and skill to accurately and quickly transfer data from paper, electronic files, and other sources into digital formats. We provide a range of services, such as data entry, document conversion, and data capture services, that enable our customers to streamline their operations. Our services are customizable and cost-effective, allowing businesses to maximize their productivity and efficiency.&nbsp;<br />\r\nWe always provide our customers with the highest quality while maintaining security and confidentiality. Our experienced data entry professionals can help businesses improve their workflow and save time and resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fast, Secure and Accurate&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Online Data Entry Services are fast, secure, and accurate. We understand data accuracy&#39;s importance to you, and we are committed to offering the most reliable services. Our team of experienced data entry professionals provides the highest quality services. We use the latest technology and processes to ensure your data is secure and up to the mark. We provide quick turnaround times, and our services are designed to meet the highest levels of accuracy and security. We use the safest protocols available and are continuously working on ways to improve our services. With our Online Data Entry Services, you can rest assured that your data is safe.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '2022-12-20 06:33:45', NULL),
(8, 'Offline Data Entry', 0, 'For Mainpage - Offline Data Entry', '2', '<h2>Fast and Fluent Offline Data Entry Services By DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DiMarz provides fast and fluent offline data entry services to businesses of all sizes. We understand the importance of accuracy and speed. Our data entry experts use the latest technology and efficient processes to ensure the highest quality of service. Our services include data entry from paper documents, scanned documents, PDFs, and other offline sources. We also provide data entry of customer information, product information, financial data, and more.&nbsp;<br />\r\nDiMarz&#39;s comprehensive suite of offline data entry services allows you to save time and money while gaining access to accurate and up-to-date data. Our services are secure and reliable.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>From Data Cleaning to Conversion, You Can Count on Us</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer a comprehensive range of offline data entry services, from data cleaning to conversion. Our team can handle any data entry with accuracy, speed, and efficiency. We use innovative technology and data security measures to ensure that all data is handled properly. We can process large volumes of data quickly, making us an ideal choice for businesses requiring quick and accurate data entry. Our reliable and cost-effective services make us the perfect solution for any organization that needs to manage its data. We are always willing to customize our services to meet the needs of our clients.</p>', '2022-12-20 06:34:16', NULL),
(9, 'Frontend Development', 0, 'For Mainpage - Frontend Development', '5', '<h2>Create Appealing Web Experience With Our Frontend Development Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DiMarz Front-End Development allows businesses to create powerful web experiences tailored to their company&#39;s specific needs. Our experienced team of professionals works closely with clients to understand their vision and develop a framework to bring it to life. With us, businesses can create stunning web layouts and interactive UI elements that make their sites stand out. We use the latest frameworks to ensure our clients can access the most up-to-date features and responsiveness. Our team also provides ongoing support and can help with troubleshooting and maintenance. Our developers are dedicated and experienced enough to fulfill your any kind&nbsp;of expectations. With DiMarz, businesses can trust that their web development needs are in the best hands.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Take Your Website to the Next Level</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As a business, it is essential to have an attractive and user-friendly front-end design for your website to attract and retain customers. At DiMarz, we have a team of experienced web designers dedicated to creating responsive and attractive front-end designs. Our structures are built to be user-friendly, allowing your customers to navigate and interact with your website easily. With our help, you can give your customers a seamless and enjoyable user experience while creating an attractive and eye-catching website that will attract more customers. We understand the importance of user-friendliness and look of&nbsp;a web application. We will ensure that you will get a responsive frontend development of your website which will meet your goals.</p>', '2022-12-20 06:35:05', '2022-12-23 11:17:19'),
(10, 'Backend Development', 0, 'For Mainpage - Backend Development', '2', '<h2>Get Professional Backend Development Services from DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide Professional Backend Development Services to help businesses increase efficiency and reduce costs. Our team can design custom solutions to fit your specific needs. We use the latest technologies and industry best practices to ensure that your backend architecture is secure, reliable, and efficient. We provide various services, from full-stack development to data storage and management. Our solutions are designed to be scalable so your organization can grow confidently. We guarantee satisfaction with our services and are committed to providing you with the best customer experience possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Stable, Responsive and Secure&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer a comprehensive backend development service that is secure, reliable, and responsive. Our team of experienced and certified developers is dedicated to providing a robust, highly-scalable, and extensible backend system that can meet any business&rsquo;s needs. We have deep expertise in developing databases, database applications, web services, microservices, and APIs. Our backend services prioritize security and quality assurance, ensuring that your data is protected and that performance is consistent. Our agile and responsive development processes allow us to quickly and effectively meet your needs.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-12-20 06:35:52', NULL),
(11, 'Web Application', 0, 'For Mainpage - Web Application', '2', '<h2>Custom Web Application Development Services By DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DiMarz provides top-of-the-line custom web application development services. With a team of experienced software developers and designers, We are dedicated to creating custom web applications suited to each client&rsquo;s needs. Our team works hard to understand each client&rsquo;s business model and goals and create a web application to help them achieve their objectives. We also provide maintenance and support services to ensure that our applications remain secure and functioning correctly. With a commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, DiMarz delivers a comprehensive suite of services to meet the clients&rsquo; web application development needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Build a Custom Website That Suits Your Needs&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We understand the importance of having an effective website that accurately reflects the personality and goals of your business. Our team of experienced designers and developers can create a custom website that will serve your needs perfectly. From the initial planning to the final launch, we are here to help you create a website that will capture the attention of your target audience. We will ensure that your website is optimized for search engines, is fully responsive and can handle a high traffic volume. We will work with you every step of the way to ensure that your website truly reflects the vision you have for your business. Our goal is to ensure that your website is an effective digital asset that will help you succeed in achieving your business goals.</p>', '2022-12-20 06:36:52', NULL),
(12, 'Photo Editing', 0, 'For Mainpage - Photo Editing', '2', '<h2>Creative &amp; Professional Photo Editing Services Company || With a Focus on Results</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Regarding photo editing services, the results are the most critical measure of success. For those looking for a professional photo editing services company that focuses on results, look no further than our Creative &amp; Professional Designer. We&#39;ve been providing editing services for years, and our clients have always been delighted with the results. We offer a wide range of professional photo editing services, from basic color correction, natural shadow, clipping path, Photo restoration, image masking, and retouching to advanced creative effects. Whether you&#39;re looking to give your photos a professional touch or to create something truly unique and eye-catching, we have the skills and expertise to make it happen. Our experienced photo editors have worked on projects for various industries, including fashion, media, and advertising. We understand the importance of producing high-quality, professional-looking images and take great pride in our work.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Services Provided by our Design Experts</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we pride ourselves on having an outstanding team of highly-skilled professionals who are experienced in utilizing Adobe Photoshop and other Adobe Creative Cloud software. Our photoshop experts have experience in providing various services ranging from photo retouching and editing to digital art and illustrations to creating marketing materials and graphics for web and print. Our team is well-versed in the appropriate techniques for creating professional-grade images for any project. We understand the importance of having high-quality photos and delivering the best results possible with each of our projects. With our commitment to quality work, we help our clients achieve their desired results.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-12-20 06:37:40', NULL),
(13, 'Professional Design', 0, 'For Mainpage - Professional Design', '2', '<h2>Outstanding Graphic Design Gathers Customer&#39;s Attention</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphic design has always been an essential part of a company&#39;s image. A well-done graphic design can set the tone for the company and help it stand out from its competitors. It can also help customers trust the company because they know the design is well-made and looks professional. Good graphic design can be simple or complex, depending on the company&#39;s needs. It can create logos, website designs, advertisements, and more. There are many different types of graphic designers, but all have one common goal: to improve customer experience with the company. Outstanding graphic design can help make a positive impression on your current and potential customers, which is why it is essential to ensure that your graphics reflect the values of your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\nMake Your Business Look More Professional With DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphic design is the art of creating visual content to communicate messages. Designers work with text and images to create visual compositions that convey ideas and tell stories. The field of graphic design is incredibly versatile, allowing designers to work in various industries, including advertising, publishing, branding, and web design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you need a little help creating the perfect design for your business, our team of graphic designers is here to help! Our team will work with you to understand your vision and create designs that reflect your brand identity. Dimarz offers a range of services to suit your needs, whether you need a new logo, some marketing materials, or even just a few tweaks to your existing designs.</p>', '2022-12-20 06:38:15', '2022-12-22 12:11:10');
