(5, 1, 'Do You Offer Free Consultation?', 'We Offer 30 Min free Consultation. Our experienced consultants can identify the problem and suggest appropriate solutions for your business and find out the steps you should take before setting a goal.', NULL, '2022-12-15 11:19:14', NULL),
(6, 1, 'Will you provide a detailed report ?', 'We Provide reports for each of our services. Our Specialist team is always ready to deliver your reports. They provide you with daily, weekly, monthly reports according to your services.', NULL, '2022-12-15 11:19:27', NULL),
(7, 2, 'What Type of SEO is Best?', 'There is no term such as Good SEO or Bad SEO. It totally depends on the type of SEO you are conducting to reach your goals. You can conduct a successful SEO campaign if you have a clear vision of what you want and what you are trying to achieve.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:03:01', '2022-12-19 07:07:41'),
(8, 2, 'Does SEO Really Work for Small Businesses?', 'Yes, SEO does work for small businesses. In fact, many small businesses are holding on to SEO to reach their goals. SEO helps a business to grow and market their products without spending a big fortune. The good thing about SEO is you can target your customers and generate a decent result than the traditional marketing systems and it\'s also pocket friendly too.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:04:58', NULL),
(9, 2, 'How Many Hours Does SEO Take?', 'Let’s make one thing clear, SEO isn’t a rocket science which can tell when you will see results. The result may come visible within 2 hours to 1 year. It totally depends on some major factors like website crawlability and indexing rate, competitiveness of the keywords, competitors and so on. SEO is a package of efforts put into a website to climb the Search ranks through different techniques. So, no one can guarantee an exact time for a SEO to be completed. But good news is, some results may come visible within 2-3 weeks after conducting a SEO campaign on a website.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:05:15', NULL),
(10, 2, 'What is The First Thing To Do Before Doing SEO?', 'The first and most important thing to do before doing SEO is to clear the visions and goals you want to achieve through SEO. You can’t expect a good result if you don’t even know what you are doing and what your end goal is after implementing SEO practices to your website. So, before going for SEO services, make it clear to yourself what you want to achieve with SEO.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:05:31', NULL),
(11, 2, 'What makes a good SEO strategy?', 'It Depends on various terms. To make a good SEO strategy, you must first clear one thing and that is your end goal. Then you can plan your strategy according to your goals and what you want to achieve. But technically, a good SEO strategy consists of proper implementation of best SEO practices in respect of the search engine policies.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:05:49', NULL),
(12, 2, 'How Can I Improve My SEO Traffic in 30 Days?', 'It depends on the condition of a website and the SEO practices conducted on the website before. If everything goes fine, you may see a major difference in SEO traffic within or less than 30 days. But it may take more time to get SEO traffic to your website if the website is not performing well or SEO is not up to the mark. So, the only way to improve SEO traffic in 30 days is to implement the best SEO strategies possible.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:06:08', NULL),
(13, 2, 'How Long Should I Pay For SEO?', 'SEO is a long-term process. There is no end to SEO practices as Google and other search engines are changing their algorithm and becoming more efficient day by day. Being a changing sector, you have to work on your SEO until you want to operate your online business. But sometimes it may differ from case to case. As in, if you want local visibility, then 2-3 months of SEO campaign is good enough for you. But corporate or enterprise level SEO has no end as it is a competitive sector and you have to maintain good SEO practices to survive in the competition.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:06:22', NULL),
(14, 2, 'Do You Take Custom Offers?', 'Yes, we do take custom offers. You can go through our pricings in the page. In case, you need to add or cut some services, you can do that through customization.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:06:39', NULL),
(15, 6, 'How will technical SEO work?', 'Technical SEO is optimizing a website for Google search to improve its visibility and ranking. It involves improving the site\'s architecture, code, content, and other factors influencing Google\'s ability to index and crawl the site.', NULL, '2022-12-19 08:46:33', NULL),
(16, 6, 'What Do You Need to Start Working?', 'We need your website link, target location, and login info for the website to get started.', NULL, '2022-12-19 08:46:49', '2022-12-23 15:14:18'),
(17, 6, 'What are the major parts of technical SEO?', 'The major parts are page titles, title tags, HTTP headers, XML sitemaps, 301 redirects, and metadata.', NULL, '2022-12-19 08:47:15', '2022-12-23 15:16:19'),
(18, 6, 'Do You Provide Other SEO Services?', 'We provide all types of seo services. We provide On page seo, page seo,  ,site audit, and complete professional seo services. You can choose any type of service which you want for your website.', NULL, '2022-12-19 08:47:28', '2022-12-23 15:17:21'),
