(20, 3, 'What do I need to get started?', 'I need several pieces of content - text, images, etc. And, your mailchimp/ or any other email sending account login (if you already have one) to start.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:01:40', NULL),
(22, 3, 'Why should I hire you?', 'We  are experienced email marketer who has extensive knowledge of email marketing platforms and strategies. We understand the importance of creating engaging emails that attract and convert prospects into customers. Dimarz highly organized, skilled in customer segmentation and targeting, and have a creative eye for email design.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:02:06', '2022-12-29 17:30:39'),
(23, 3, 'How can I improve my email marketing open rate?', '. To increase open rates, it is important to start by ensuring your emails are optimized for engagement. This includes tailoring emails for your target audience, crafting subject lines that are concise and eye-catching, and understanding what time of day your emails should be sent.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:02:18', '2022-12-29 17:43:35'),
(24, 3, 'What are the best email marketing tools?', 'One of the best email marketing tools is MailChimp, which allows users to quickly and easily create, send, and track emails. It\'s user-friendly and offers comprehensive reporting and analytics, making it an ideal choice for small businesses.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:02:30', '2022-12-29 17:36:38'),
