(33, 8, 'What is the process of on-page SEO optimization?', 'The first step is to conduct keyword research to identify which keywords will most likely bring users to your site. Once you have a list of target keywords, you can then start revising your website\'s title tags, meta descriptions, header tags, and body content to include these keywords. In addition, it\'s also essential to ensure that your website\'s URLs are clean and descriptive and that your site is easy to navigate.', NULL, '2022-12-19 11:19:43', NULL),
