(4, 1, 2, 'Technical SEO', 'technical-seo-services', 'Technical SEO improve the way your website is crawled, rendered, and indexed', '<h2>The Reason Why you Will Need Technical SEO</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Technical SEO is the initial and one of the most important parts of a SEO campaign. It is the process where all technical issues are fixed in a website for better user experience and better ranking. Having problems in a website user experience is a major issue for the traffic base as bounce rates get higher and you may even get penalized by google for delivering poor experience. So, it is essential to run a technical SEO on your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How Technical Optimizations Affect Your SEO?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As per recent SEO statistics, if a website takes more than 10 seconds to load then the bounce rate will <strong>shoot up to 123%</strong>. So, it is clear that Google clearly puts user experience first. Technical optimizations solely work for this particular purpose. We always take technical SEO seriously. Regarding that fact, our team will work thoroughly on your website&#39;s inner issues which are negatively affecting your site&#39;s user experience and performances. By fixing the technical problems you will see a drastic rank promotion in Google.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Get a Free Technical Audit</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In our service, we cover the most important parts of the technical SEO which are directly connected with core web vitals like Speed Optimization, Fix Redirection issues, Image Optimization, HTTPS Setup, Minify/Remove unused scripts, AMP Setup and others. Get a free Technical Audit from us and see what&#39;s going wrong with your website.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Technical SEO Services', '<p>Technical SEO is the practice of improving the crawlability and indexability of your website so that search engines can more easily find and understand your content. We make sure that your site is well-structured and easy to navigate. Investing in Technical SEO services are essential to improving your online visibility and driving traffic to your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Technical SEO Services Include the following:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Website Audit</li>\r\n	<li>Google Penalty Check</li>\r\n	<li>Crawlability &amp; Indexability</li>\r\n	<li>SSL Certificate (HTTPS) Enforceability</li>\r\n	<li>XML Sitemap</li>\r\n	<li>404 &amp; 301 Redirection</li>\r\n	<li>Robot text files optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Search Console integration</li>\r\n	<li>Fix website bugs, issues and errors</li>\r\n	<li>Site speed optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Image Optimization</li>\r\n</ul>', 4, '<h2>Why Choose Dimarz For Technical SEO on Your Websites?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide in-depth analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Improved the performance of your website</li>\r\n	<li>Fixed your Website all Errors&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Bring more organic traffic</li>\r\n	<li>Make sure that your websites will perform better</li>\r\n</ul>', 6, 6, 5, 1, '2022-12-19 09:09:02', '2022-12-23 13:38:46'),
(5, 1, 3, 'Email Template', 'email-template', 'Directly Reach Your  potential Target Audience with the email marketing', '<h2>A Well Designed Email Template Ensures Maximum Succession</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Email templates is one kind of HTML coded design which allows you to add media or other things like images or links which greatly reflects your business. A good email template makes your statement stand out more than others. So, it is important to design a gorgeous email template to get noticed.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What Factors make a Good Email Template?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In order to create an effective email template design, it is important to consider the different factors that affect how well a template will perform. This includes the recipient&#39;s unique needs, the tone, and the content of the email. We always consider these facts when designing our client&rsquo;s templates. Our team will design email templates which will convey your message properly to the targeted audiences.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Get Your Email Templates Done With DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide Email Template Designing Service. Our service covers both small businesses and large organizations. We will create custom email templates that are perfect for any occasion. These templates are easy to use and add value to your emails. When it comes to Email Template Designing, we know what it takes to make sure your sendernews looks great.</p>', 4, 'Email Template Services', '<p>Email templates geared towards any device with an email client allow you to send customized emails that function on any device.An email template is a pre-defined, standard e-mail that can include content like images or text, depending on the design. If your email template looks good &amp; responsive, you will retain your targeted customer. So every email template should be responsive. We will design and code responsive Email Templates and Signatures for your demand. We can create HTML/CSS inline tables, adaptable for desktops, tablets and mobiles.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Email Templates Services Includes :&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Optimize for desktop and mobile devices.</li>\r\n	<li>HTML email template that&#39;s professional, responsive, and clickable.</li>\r\n	<li>No copying and pasting is allowed.</li>\r\n	<li>Valid HTML, Inline CSS</li>\r\n	<li>Major Email Client Compatible</li>\r\n	<li>MailChimp Compatible</li>\r\n</ul>', 5, '<h2>Why Do You Choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Safe &amp; secure</li>\r\n	<li>High-quality work</li>\r\n	<li>Customized Design</li>\r\n	<li>Fast &amp; Supper Communication Skills</li>\r\n</ul>', 7, 8, 5, 1, '2022-12-19 10:40:32', '2022-12-24 11:06:52'),
(6, 1, 2, 'On-Page SEO', 'on-page-seo-services', 'Earn more organic  traffic  from search engines with on-page Optimization.', '<h2>Good On-Page SEO Leads To Better Rank</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>On-Page SEO is the key to a healthy and successful SEO campaign. Properly maintaining on-page checklists &nbsp;paves the way to a better ranking opportunity on SERPs. <strong>Search Engine Rankings are 70% dependent</strong> on website&rsquo;s inner optimizations and contents. Unoptimized and bad website structure will lead to lower ranking positions and eventually get penalized by search engines like google.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why On-Page Plays a Crucial Part in SEO?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are many important factors of SEO which only can be done in On-Page. Some of them are content optimization, keyword research, url, meta tags, headings, alt.tag optimizations and more. Content is the king. This can be only done through On-Page SEO. We have a specialized time who will go through your on-page strategy build ups and forge a competitive strategy to rank your page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Get Your On-Page Done By Professionals</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we provide professional on-page SEO services that can help your website reach its full potential. Our team of experienced SEO professionals will analyze your website&#39;s content, structure, and performance to identify key areas of improvement. We will create an effective strategy tailored to your business needs. Our services will help you achieve higher search engine rankings, increased website traffic, and conversions. Our experienced SEO experts will also provide you with ongoing support and advice to ensure that your website remains.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'On Page SEO Services', '<p>On-Page SEO Service is the best way to improve your website&#39;s visibility and organic search ranking. It involves optimizing your website&#39;s title, meta tags, header tags, images, and other elements to make it more visible and attractive to search engines. It al