(52, 1, 1, 'Web Research', 'web-research', 'With Top-Notch Web Research Gain Insight into Your Target Audience and Develop Strategies to Reach Them', '<h2>Why Do You Need Web Research Service?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Web research reveals a wide range of helpful information that businesses and organizations may use in a variety of ways. When you are aware of the vital information of your counterparts, customers, prospects, and competitors, you can easily plan the strategies to expand your reach, increase your sales and gain an edge over your competitors.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Web Research Can Benefit Your Bottom Line!</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>By digging through the massive amounts of information from different sources Web analytics professionals can provide you with informative insights while helping you enhance your prospective customer. With our web research services, you will get a Significant reduction in marketing costs, Better comprehension of the competitors, and Wider reach into the target markets across the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Get ahead of the curve with Our Web research&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our web research services offer an easy solution for all your online and offline research. We have a professional team who are experts on Leads, Property, documents, Products, Events, Financial &amp; different types of Business or company research. We offer completely customized and highly cost-efficient services to aid businesses with the right set of information that they are seeking in the desired format. Run effective web research with DiMarz and get ahead in the competition.</p>', 4, 'Web Research', '<p>Web Research services are invaluable for businesses looking to get the most out of their online presence. Our services offer the ability to collect and analyze data from the web to identify trends, patterns, and opportunities for improvement. By utilizing web research, businesses can gain insight into their target audience and develop strategies to reach them.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\