(55, 1, 3, 'MailChimp Campaign', 'mailchimp-campaign', 'Automate Your Email Sending Process More Efficiently and Professionally', '<h2>Why Use Mailchimp For Email Marketing?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Mailchimp is a free email marketing platform that allows you to create and send newsletters, which can reach a large audience. By using Mailchimp, you can increase your list size and get more leads in less time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What Are The Benefits of Using Mailchimp?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mailchimp is a popular email marketing platform that offers a wide range of benefits for businesses who needs to send&nbsp; huge amount of emails within a short time. Some of the benefits of using Mailchimp includes:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1)</strong> Increased reach and engagement with your customers: Mailchimp allows businesses to send out unlimited automated emails to their subscribers, which can reach a wider audience. This leads to increased engagement with customers, as they are more likely to click through and take action on the email content.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>2) </strong>Reduced cost: Mailchimp has an extremely low monthly price point, which means that it is affordable for small businesses who want to use its features. This also leads to increased efficiency as fewer resources are needed to run the campaign, making it more cost-effective overall.<br />\r\n<strong>3) </strong>Have a good overview of what&rsquo;s going on: With mailchimp, you can keep track of all of the data including open rate, bounce rate, how many people it has reached and who has opened your mail, etc. With this information, you can take next actions according to the data provided.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Run Mailchimp Campaign With Us</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Email Marketing Coordinators will run an effective campaign through Mailchimp which will bring better results. Our team is dedicated to creating campaigns that are easy to manage and profitable.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'MailChimp Campaign', '<p>Mailchimp is an