(58, 1, 2, 'Monthly SEO Service', 'monthly-seo-service', 'Take Your Website To The Top of SERP With Monthly SEO', '<h2>Just Having a Website Isn&rsquo;t Enough, It Needs To Be Search Engine Optimized</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are many websites out there on the internet which are not getting the expected results. That&rsquo;s because their websites are not fully search engine optimized. An optimized website can bring a ton of potential customers or audiences to your website without spending extra money. And a fully search engine optimized website ranks top of a search engine which also is admired by people because search engines tend to rank websites which add value to their audiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How Can You Benefit From SEO?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>By doing SEO on your website, you will have a better chance to rank your pages on top of search engine ranking positions. It will enable you to get exposure for your site to a wide range of audience who are looking for things relevant to your niche. As per AHrefs, 68% online experience starts with a search engine. So, there are higher chances for your business to get more qualified leads and customers. Regarding this, a stat from Hubspot shows that <strong>SEO leads have a 14.6% close rate.</strong> That&rsquo;s why having a fully optimized website is really important for a website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Get Full SEO Service From DiMarz?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, our professional SEO consultants will take care of your website and help in order to reach the top spot of your desired search engine. We have a specialized SEO team who are looking over the different sectors of SEO as in Technical, On-Page, Off-Page, Content Writing, etc. Together we are committed to rank your site to the first page of any search engine. Start Your SEO campaign with us and rest easy!<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Monthly SEO Service', '<p>Seo is the practice of optimizing your web pages to make them reach a high position in the search results of Google and other search engines. There are many types of seo. On page optimization, &nbsp;Technical Seo, Off page Seo,link building,local seo etc. We provided you full seo service in this package.We will ensure you that your websites will rank better and get more traffic after our service.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our SEO Services :<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>TECHNICAL:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Website Audit</li>\r\n	<li>Google Penalty Check</li>\r\n	<li>Crawlability &amp; Indexability</li>\r\n	<li>Canonicalization</li>\r\n	<li>SSL Certificate (HTTPs) Enforceability</li>\r\n	<li>XML Sitemap</li>\r\n	<li>404 &amp; 301 Redirection</li>\r\n	<li>Robot txt files optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Search Console integration</li>\r\n	<li>Analytics, heatmap setup</li>\r\n	<li>Fix website bugs ,issues and errors</li>\r\n	<li>Site speed optimization<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>ON-PAGE:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Optimize Meta Description</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize Heading (H1, H2, H3) Tags</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize Image ALT Tags</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize Meta Tag</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize URLs</li>\r\n	<li>Schema Markup</li>\r\n	<li>Fix duplicate content &amp; stop words from URLs</li>\r\n	<li>Competitor Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Organic Keyword analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Content planning, Enhance &amp; improvement</li>\r\n	<li>Rank branded &amp; non-branded keywords</li>\r\n	<li>Keyword Rank tracking &amp; Optimizing<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>OFF-PAGE:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High-quality backlinks (50-100/Month)</li>\r\n	<li>Branded property optimisation</li>\r\n	<li>Google My Business optimisation</li>\r\n	<li>Integrate known search engines (Bing, Yandex, Google)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Boost ranking</li>\r\n	<li>Organic keywords ranking&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Competitor backlink analysis &amp; link building opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Email reach</li>\r\n</ul>', 58, '<h2>Why did you choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% elaborated Report</li>\r\n	<li>We improved the ranking of your web site.</li>\r\n	<li>Authority profiles Backlinks</li>\r\n	<li>High Quality Link building</li>\r\n	<li>On time delivery and 24/7 client support<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 12, 58, 5, 1, '2022-12-20 15:37:23', '2022-12-23 13:42:07'),
(59, 1, 2, 'Local SEO', 'local-seo', 'Increase Your Websites Local Visibility', '<h2>Importance of Local SEO</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Local SEO is important for businesses of any size that wish to increase their online visibility locally. It helps to target local customers by optimizing content for local searches, which helps businesses to show up higher in search engine results. Local SEO is also beneficial for businesses because it helps to increase the relevance of their content and boost the chances of being found by potential customers. Additionally, local SEO is an important way to build authority in the local market and establish a credible presence in the local community. When businesses use local SEO effectively, they will see an increase in both website traffic and leads. It makes local SEO a valuable asset for any business that wishes to grow its online presence and reach its local audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How We Will Locally Optimize Your Visibility</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Local SEO is an important aspect of a business in today&#39;s competitive landscape. It is the optimization method of a website to make it more visible for local searches. This optimization includes creating local content that matches the keywords used by potential customers when searching for a business, ensuring the website is accurately listed in local directories, and utilizing local link-building tactics to increase exposure. Local SEO also focuses on optimizing content for mobile devices, as most local searches are conducted via a mobile device. Additionally, local SEO involves optimizing for location-based services such as Google My Business, Apple Maps, and Yelp. By implementing local SEO strategies, businesses can increase their visibility and reach more local customers, leading to increased sales and growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Boost Your Local Authority with DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide Local SEO services for businesses looking to leverage their local presence and reach more customers. Our experienced team of SEO professionals can help you create an effective local search strategy that will increase your visibility and improve your ranking in local search results. We specialize in optimizing websites for local searches, providing customized solutions suited to your business needs. Our services include keyword research and analysis, content optimization, website optimization, and link building. We also provide ongoing tracking and analysis to ensure the success of your local SEO efforts. With our help, you can ensure that the right people will see your business at the right time.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Local SEO Services', '<p>Businesses can profit at a larger margin if they locally optimize their website for their local people. Local SEO can help you in that matter. In this process, we locally rank your keywords to your desired location so that people around there can get access to your website.Local SEO also monitors the business&#39;s search engine rankings and makes adjustments as needed to ensure that customers can find the business online. Overall, local SEO is important for businesses looking to stay competitive in the digital age.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What to Expect from Dimarz Local SEO Services :&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>On Site Optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Google My Business Optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Local Citations</li>\r\n	<li>GMB Posts</li>\r\n	<li>Link Building (Local)</li>\r\n	<li>Schema Markup</li>\r\n	<li>Content Planning</li>\r\n	<li>Bi-Monthly Report<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 59, '<h2>Why choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% elaborated Report</li>\r\n	<li>We improved the ranking of your web site.</li>\r\n	<li>Authority profiles Backlinks</li>\r\n	<li>High Quality Link building</li>\r\n	<li>On time delivery and 24/7 client support<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 11, 59, 5, 1, '2022-12-20 15:52:51', '2022-12-23 16:03:05'),
(60, 1, 5, 'Blog Content', 'blog-content', 'Through blogging, customers can discover more about your business.', '<h2>Blog That Gets Traffic And Builds Authority In Your Niche</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Blogs are a great way to share your ideas and insights. But increasing the frequency and quality of your blog posts can be daunting. It has become a trendy thing in today&#39;s world as the number of affiliate marketers and bloggers are increasing drastically. Blogging has become a great source of income in recent years. There are many factors that come along with it like writing authenticity, hierarchy, topical authority, SEO, etc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Things To Consider While Writing Blogs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a few things you should consider while writing a blog post. These include topics you want to address, the tone of your post, and whether or not you want to use images. Other important factors should be taken into consideration like writing intent, topical authoritativeness, effective introductions and conclusions, SEO, etc. Our writers are well versed in these terms while writing blogs for clients. We will provide you standard, error-free and SEO friendly blogs which will engage more audiences to read your piece of content.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Start Blogging With DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our easy-to-read style and engaging blog writing will keep your readers engaged, even on the most difficult assignments. We understand the importance of SEO, and we will also make sure that your content gets fully search-engine optimized.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Blog Content Services', '<p>Blog content writing is an essential part of any online marketing strategy. It involves creating engaging, informative, and entertaining content for readers of a blog or website. By creating content that meets the specific needs of the target audience, content writers can help to drive traffic to your blog website. Content writers can advise how to structure the content for maximum reach and impact. Additionally, content writers can research and curate content related to a business&#39;s industry, helping to establish the company as an authority in its field.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Blog Content Writing Services Including :&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"display:none\">&nbsp;</span>Depth keyword research &amp; Implementation</li>\r\n	<li>SEO-optimized posts</li>\r\n	<li>Header Tags Optimized</li>\r\n	<li>Titles &amp; Meta Descriptions Provided</li>\r\n</ul>', 60, '<h2>Why Choose DiMarz for your Blog Websites?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We write content that performs long-term</li>\r\n	<li>We write 100% manual writing</li>\r\n	<li>We don&#39;t use AI tools</li>\r\n	<li>We are honest about our work</li>\r\n</ul>', 17, 60, 3, 1, '2022-12-21 12:01:06', '2022-12-21 12:01:06'),
(61, 1, 5, 'Websites CopyWriting', 'websites-copywriting', 'Great copywriting services are aware of the need to convey a sense of urgency in their writing.', '<h2>Why You Need SEO Friendly &amp; Engaging Website Copywriting Service</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A website landing page should be written in a way which should be both optimized for search engine visibility and engaging for readers. Only professional copywriters can craft content that highlights your company&rsquo;s strengths and appeals to potential customers. A website copy is written to be more easily found through organic searches and contains keywords and phrases that will draw more visitors to your site. Additionally, the content is written engagingly, encouraging readers to take action, such as visiting your business, signing up for a newsletter, or purchasing a product. With an SEO Friendly and Engaging Website Copywriting Service, you can reach a wider audience while ensuring your business is seen as a trusted source.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Main Aspects of Website Copywriting</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Website copywriting is creating persuasive, compelling, and engaging content for websites. It is an essential tool for businesses to bring in more customers, gain more conversions, and generate higher profits. The main aspects of website copywriting include the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Keyword research.</li>\r\n	<li>SEO writing.</li>\r\n	<li>Creating persuasive calls to action.</li>\r\n	<li>Optimizing content structure.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensuring the content is clear and concise.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Keyword research focuses on understanding the words and phrases used by potential customers to find the business&rsquo;s services or products. SEO writing is the process of creating content that is optimized for search engine visibility. Creating persuasive calls to action encourages visitors to take the desired action. Optimizing content structure helps the user experience by providing a clear message and directing the user&rsquo;s focus. Lastly, ensuring the content is clear and concise for readers.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Websites CopyWriting Services', '<p>Website Copywriting is the process of producing written content for websites. This content needs to be engaging and attention-grabbing while still conveying the right message and purpose of the website. It should be written in a tone that reflects the target audience and should be easy to read. It should also be completed to the website&#39;s goals, whether to increase sales, inform customers, or build an online presence. Professional website copywriters should have a good understanding of the target audience and the website&#39;s goals and be able to craft unique and captivating content. They should also have a good understanding of SEO and the ability to craft content for desktop and mobile website versions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Website Copywriting Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Keyword Implementation</li>\r\n	<li>Engaging Writing</li>\r\n	<li>Write For Any Landing Pages</li>\r\n	<li>Eye-Catchy Title</li>\r\n	<li>Basic SEO Setup</li>\r\n	<li>Writing Meta Tags and Schema (Premium Package Only)</li>\r\n</ul>', 61, '<h2>Why Choose us</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% unique and updated according to the latest trends</li>\r\n	<li>No grammatical errors/correct sentence structure</li>\r\n	<li>Free of Any Kind of Spun or Plagiarism</li>\r\n	<li>Proofreading Through Premium Tools</li>\r\n	<li>SEO Friendly</li>\r\n	<li>Timely delivery</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 availability</li>\r\n	<li>Full customer support and</li>\r\n	<li>Mulltiple revisions until satisfaction<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 18, 61, 3, 1, '2022-12-21 12:28:39', '2022-12-21 12:28:39'),
(62, 1, 5, 'Social Media Content', 'social-media-content', 'With a social media presence that engages, inspires your audience, you can give your brand an identity.', '<h2>Create Powerful Social Media Content That Will Get Your Customers Interested&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Social Media is a very powerful platform where your content creates a great impact. It can be used to build relationships, promote your brand, and connect with customers. However, you need to understand the risks and benefits of using social media to create content otherwise your content will have no impact on your readers whether it is a long post or just a single caption.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Social Media Contents Matter The Most?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Social media has become an essential tool for relationships and communication. The most important thing social media can do is provide people with reliable and up-to-date information, which is why it&rsquo;s essential that content on social media should be accurate and relevant. Keeping that in mind, we will craft content that will be genuine, well researched and add value to your audiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Craft Impactful Social Media Contents With DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our professional social media writing service provides quality, engaging content to help you stand out. Plus, our team is flexible and available to work with any social media platform, whether an article or caption.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Social Media Content Services', '<p>Social media content has become a valuable asset for businesses and individuals. It can help to build relationships, attract new customers, and spread awareness about a product or service.By using social media content to inform and entertain, businesses can now gain followers and build a loyal customer base.A social media content writer can help you create high-quality content that is both entertaining and informative.So hiring a social media content writer is a great way to ensure your company is reaching its target audience in the most effective way possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Social Media Content Writing Services :</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Scheduling/Posting creative and relevant posts/content.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Optimized social media description</li>\r\n	<li>For all social media, specific formatting and optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Product descriptions based on ads</li>\r\n	<li>Ad copywriting</li>\r\n	<li>Hashtag research &amp; indexing.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Engaging and well-written Captions.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Keyword optimized content</li>\r\n	<li>Paid stock images and visual content for posts.</li>\r\n</ul>', 62, '<h2>Why Choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Engaging campaign content</li>\r\n	<li>Listen and analyze</li>\r\n	<li>Following creativity and uniqueness</li>\r\n</ul>', 19, 62, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 12:45:13', '2022-12-24 10:57:42');
