(75, 2, 7, 'PDF to Word/Excel', 'pdf-to-wordexcel', 'Convert Your PDF File into Word/Excel Whenever You Need', '<h2>Why Do You Need PDF to Word Conversion?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>PDF to Word conversion is essential for any business to maximize efficiency and streamline its workflow. PDF documents are often more secure than Word documents; however, they are less user-friendly and can cause delays in the editing process. Word documents are much easier to edit, allowing collaborations to happen faster and more seamlessly. PDF to Word conversion allows businesses to convert PDF files into Word documents, making it easier to share, edit and collaborate in real time. Additionally, it reduces the risk of data loss when transferring documents between different formats, as it preserves the original formatting of the PDF file. By utilizing PDF to Word conversion, businesses can increase productivity and ensure their documents are secure and up-to-date.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why our PDF to Word Conversion Services are Different</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer comprehensive PDF to Word conversion services for individuals and businesses. Our team is highly trained in the latest technology, allowing us to deliver the highest quality conversion results. We are fast, reliable, secure, and cost-effective. Our service preserves the original formatting, layout, and graphics, ensuring that the converted Word document looks like the original PDF file. We also offer additional features such as password protection, encryption, and watermarking when required. We also ensure that all converted documents are 100% virus-free and that the security of our client&rsquo;s information is always protected.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Convert Your PDF to Word With Professionals</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we take pride in providing a fast and accurate conversion process so you can quickly and easily use your converted documents. We guarantee a secure and private conversion process and will never share your documents with third parties. Our experts can answer any questions about the conversion process or our services. We strive to provide the best quality PDF to Word Conversion services and ensure that your documents are converted correctly.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'PDF to Word Services', '<p>PDF to Word/Excel conversion is a convenient and efficient process that can quickly turn a PDF document into an editable Word or Excel file. This technology makes it easy to take a PDF and make the necessary changes without recreating the entire document from scratch. It&#39;s also useful for organizations that need to convert large volumes of PDFs into other formats, as the process is automated and can be completed quickly.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PDF to Word / PDF to Excel&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Word / Excel / PowerPoint to PDF</li>\r\n	<li>PNG/ JPEG to Editable Document</li>\r\n	<li>Edit PDF (any type, with exact font match)</li>\r\n	<li>Remove or add images, headers, footer, backgrounds or objects</li>\r\n	<li>Design or create and insert cover page</li>\r\n	<li>Typing of scanned pdf images to word&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Create non-editable files</li>\r\n	<li>Formatting Styles, Fonts, Layout.</li>\r\n	<li>Create files protected by password.</li>\r\n	<li>Grammar or Spell Check<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 75, '<h2>Why Choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Goal Oriented</li>\r\n	<li>We provide strategic advice</li>\r\n	<li>treat your project like it&rsquo;s our own</li>\r\n	<li>Guaranteed security and confidentiality<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 36, 75, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 16:21:11', '2022-12-21 16:21:11'),
(76, 2, 7, 'Business Card Entry', 'business-card-entry', 'Enter All Your Business Card Information Into Your CRM', '<h2>Professional Business Card Entry Service By DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A professional business card entry service allows businesses to quickly and accurately enter their business card information into a digital format. This service is ideal for organizations that rely heavily on accurate contact information, such as sales, marketing, and customer service. With a professional business card entry service, all data is entered and organized precisely, ensuring accuracy and saving time and resources. The service also eliminates human error, ensuring that all contact information is correct, up to date, and organized in a manner that is easy to access. With this service, businesses can focus on other tasks and objectives with confidence that their business card information is secure and properly stored.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What Services Are Included?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Business Card Entry Service is a reliable and cost-effective way to capture critical contact data and maintain accurate customer records. Our service includes a full range of data entry services to ensure that your customer information is accurately captured and preserved. We offer</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Electronic Business Card To Client Database Conversion</li>\r\n	<li>Hard Copy Business Cards into Online System</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain Existing Business Cards</li>\r\n	<li>Business Card Format Conversion</li>\r\n	<li>Business Card Indexing</li>\r\n	<li>Update Business Card Information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Our trained professionals are dedicated to providing the highest quality service at the most competitive price. With our Business Card Entry Service, you can be assured of accurate, up-to-date customer records that will help you to grow your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Get Your Business Card Entry Done with DiMarz?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we understand how important first impressions can be. That&rsquo;s why we strive to provide the highest quality services to ensure that your business card entry needs are met with excellence. We are reliable and committed to customer satisfaction. Our team has the expertise to ensure the accuracy and quality of our services. We provide full tracking and reporting so you can be assured that your data is secure. When you choose our Business Card Entry service, you can rest assured that your tasks are in professional hands.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Business Card Entry Service', '<p><br />\r\nBusiness card entry services provide a cost-effective way of entering contact details from business cards into your customer relationship management (CRM) system. This service eliminates the tedious task of manually entering contact information while ensuring accuracy and efficiency. Through our service, businesses save time and resources, allowing them to focus on more important tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Business Card Data Entry Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Storing Information Online from Printed Business Cards</li>\r\n	<li>Business Card Format Conversion</li>\r\n	<li>Updating and Maintaining Existing Business Card Information</li>\r\n	<li>Business Card Data Scanning</li>\r\n	<li>Clean up and formatting of business card data</li>\r\n	<li>Business card categorization</li>\r\n	<li>Company logo</li>\r\n	<li>Prefixes and suffixes</li>\r\n	<li>Individual&rsquo;s name</li>\r\n	<li>Professional titles or positions</li>\r\n	<li>Telephone and fax numbers</li>\r\n	<li>Email address</li>\r\n	<li>Business URL</li>\r\n	<li>Personal or business address</li>\r\n	<li>Academic degrees<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 76, '<h2>Why choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Modernizing business cards</li>\r\n	<li>Optimizing business card data with social media sites</li>\r\n	<li>Easy accessibility of databases on devices</li>\r\n	<li>Affordable services<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 37, 76, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 16:33:18', '2022-12-21 16:33:18');
