(77, 4, 9, 'Social Media Design', 'social-media-design-services', 'Engage More Followers With Lucrative Social Media Designs', '<h2>Why Use Social Media Design Services?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are numerous benefits to using a social media design service. Because you need to be able to improve your audience&#39;s engagement on social media platforms. Additionally, this service will help you better understand your target audience and create engaging and relevant content. As a result, you&#39;ll see more followers and positive customer feedback.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What services are provided for social media design?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Social media design services offer businesses to help with their social media platforms. These services include creating a social media strategy, designing and managing a social media account, and helping with marketing and advertising campaigns. Some standard services include Branding and identity creation, Layout and design, Design consultation, Twitter marketing assistance, and Facebook marketing assistance. We provide different social design options that are customizable to your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Social Media Design Services By DiMarz Team</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A social media design company will have the expertise to create engaging and eye-catching content. You can choose the DiMarz team because they&#39;ll know how to create content that will reach the right audience and their interest. Your message will reach your targeted people interested in your niche. DiMarz can assist you with maintaining your online presence on social networks like Facebook, Instagram, Linkedin, Youtube, Twitter, Pinterest, and more.</p>', 4, 'Social Media Design Services', '<p>Social media platforms allow businesses and individuals to connect easily with customers and followers, generating leads and building brand awareness. In addition, social media design can help businesses create a more interactive online presence by creating compelling content that engages users. Using those services can be a powerful way to grow your business and reach new audiences. Social media designers can create and manage posts and content that will bring attention to your brand and drive engagement, which leads to increased followers and sales. DiMarz team works with you to understand your goals and create a strategy that will maximize the success of your campaigns.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>We design posts and covers for all social media platforms, including:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Facebook</li>\r\n	<li>Instagram</li>\r\n	<li>Twitter</li>\r\n	<li>LinkedIn</li>\r\n	<li>YouTube</li>\r\n	<li>Pinterest</li>\r\n	<li>TikTok</li>\r\n	<li>Website</li>\r\n</ul>', 77, '<h2>Why Choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our team works to make sure &nbsp;customer satisfaction is 100%.</li>\r\n	<li>Bring about original ideas to their companies.</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Social Media Design Specialists</li>\r\n</ul>', 41, 77, 3, 1, '2022-12-21 16:44:50', '2022-12-25 16:40:36'),
(78, 2, 7, 'PDF fillable forms', 'pdf-fillable-forms', 'Get Attractive and Informative PDF Forms', '<h2>Benefits of PDF Fillable Forms</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>PDF fillable forms offer numerous benefits to both businesses and individuals. For businesses, they provide an efficient and secure way to collect information and process transactions with customers. Besides, they are easy to use and distribute, as they can be easily emailed, printed, and filled out online. The data collected can be quickly organized and securely stored. For individuals, PDF fillable forms save time and effort when submitting applications, surveys, and other paperwork. They are also more reliable and secure than traditional paper forms, as they can be easily and securely saved, shared, and edited. PDF fillable forms offer businesses and individuals a convenient and secure way to collect and manage data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Features We Include in These Forms</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our PDF Fillable Forms are designed to offer you the most user-friendly experience possible. We are confident in providing our customers with a range of features that make their data entry process as efficient and straightforward as possible. Our forms are designed to be compatible with any device and come with features such as;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Text Fields</li>\r\n	<li>Check Boxes (Tick, Circle, Cross, Diamond, Square, Star)</li>\r\n	<li>Radio Buttons</li>\r\n	<li>List of Choices (Drop-down Button)</li>\r\n	<li>Print, Clear, Submit, and Save Buttons</li>\r\n	<li>Image Fields</li>\r\n	<li>Date Fields</li>\r\n	<li>Calculations (Sum, Product, Minus, Average, Minimum, Maximum, and others)</li>\r\n	<li>Formatting and validations (Number, Percentage, Date, Time, Currency, Character limit, and others)</li>\r\n	<li>Watermark (Text or Image)</li>\r\n	<li>Easily convertible to other formats</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Our forms provide an efficient, cost-effective solution for your digital document needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Choose The Best and Professional PDF Fillable Form Service</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide professional PDF fillable form services to meet the needs of our clients. Our services are designed to save time and simplify complex document processes. We provide secure online form-filling capabilities, allowing clients to quickly and accurately fill out document forms with a few clicks. Our forms are easy to use and compatible with any platform. Moreover, we provide technical support to ensure highest standards of service.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'PDF fillable forms Services', '<p>A PDF Fillable Form is an electronic document which allows users to fill in fields with information and save the document as a PDF file. Fillable forms streamline the information-gathering process, making it easier to collect data quickly and accurately. They are useful for collecting large amounts of data, such as applications, surveys, and questionnaires. Fillable forms also reduce the risk of errors, since they provide a consistent field format.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our PDF Fillable Form Creation Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Basic Buttons (Print,Clear,Save,Reset)</li>\r\n	<li>Validation (With Javascript Coding)</li>\r\n	<li>Text Fields</li>\r\n	<li>Labels</li>\r\n	<li>Split, Marge pages or Delete Pages</li>\r\n	<li>Check Boxes</li>\r\n	<li>Numeric Fields</li>\r\n	<li>Drop-down Menu</li>\r\n	<li>Radio buttons&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Image Upload</li>\r\n	<li>Calculation (Product,Average,Sum,Min,Max,Minus)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Signature (Digital Signature)</li>\r\n	<li>Date Picker</li>\r\n	<li>Watermark</li>\r\n	<li>Password Protect Fillable Form</li>\r\n	<li>Bar-code</li>\r\n	<li>Limit characters in the field</li>\r\n	<li>Internal links<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 78, '<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>One day Delivery</li>\r\n	<li>Decent quality.</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited Revisions<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 38, 78, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 16:47:37', '2022-12-21 16:47:37'),
(79, 2, 7, 'Virtual Assistant', 'virtual-assistant', 'Hire Professional Virtual Assistants to Make Your Tasks Easy', '<h2>Why Does an Organization Need Virtual Assistant?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>An organization needs a virtual assistant to help optimize operations and increase efficiency. By outsourcing tasks to a virtual assistant, the organization can free up time and resources to focus on more important tasks. Virtual assistants offer various services, such as customer support, administrative tasks, data entry, and creative assistance. By using a virtual assistant, organizations can quickly access quality assistance without needing to hire additional in-house staff. Furthermore, virtual assistants can be more cost-effective than traditional staff, as they are typically paid hourly. With the help of a virtual assistant, organizations can ensure that important tasks are completed quickly and accurately while freeing up time and resources to concentrate on more important initiatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Services We Provide</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide various services to help streamline business operations. Our professional virtual assistants offer data entry, customer service, scheduling, research, email management, and more. Not only do they help to save time and resources, but they also provide a cost-effective solution to help businesses maximize efficiency. We ensure that all our virtual assistants are trained and certified to guarantee they are equipped with the latest knowledge and techniques. Our virtual assistants are dedicated to providing quality service with a focus on accuracy and efficiency.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Hire Professional Virtual Assistants From DiMarz</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>DiMarz provides professional, reliable, and efficient virtual assistants suited to your needs. Our virtual assistants are highly trained and knowledgeable. Whether you need support with administration, bookkeeping, customer service, data entry, research, or other tasks, our virtual assistants are up to the task. We are dedicated to providing you with top-notch service and support to take the stress out of your administrative tasks and free up time to focus on innovation and growth. With DiMarz, you can be sure that you are getting the best virtual assistance available.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Virtual Assistant Services', '<p>Virtual Assistants (VAs) are a new and fast-growing workforce segment. VAs offer a range of administrative and technical support to individuals or businesses. From essential calendar management and scheduling to more complex data entry and customer service tasks, VAs can help streamline operations and provide greater efficiency.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Virtual Assistant Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Data Entry</li>\r\n	<li>Web research</li>\r\n	<li>Copy and paste</li>\r\n	<li>Lead Generation</li>\r\n	<li>Building Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Digital Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Content Migration</li>\r\n	<li>E-commerce listing</li>\r\n	<li>WordPress Website</li>\r\n	<li>Project Management</li>\r\n	<li>Shopify Dropshipping</li>\r\n	<li>Social Media Management</li>\r\n	<li>Build a database of business contacts</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft office (word, excel, notepad, ppt, etc.)<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 79, '<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Unlimited Revisions</li>\r\n	<li>Guaranteed data quality</li>\r\n	<li>100% accuracy</li>\r\n	<li>High-quality work</li>\r\n	<li>On-time delivery<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 39, 79, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 16:59:43', '2022-12-21 16:59:43'),
(80, 4, 9, 'Motion Graphic', 'motion-graphic-services', 'Beautiful Motion Graphics Designs That Will Connect Your Customers', '<h2>Importance Of Motion Graphic</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A website or brand can use motion graphics to increase visual appeal and attract customers. Motion graphics increase your brand awareness. The reason why motion graphics are so popular is that you can use it effectively to communicate information. You can show off your products or services, illustrate stories or explain concepts in an easy-to-understand way.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Do You Need Great Motion Design for Your Business?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Motion design is a way for brands to connect with customers. This type of design is also engaging and provides a unique experience for the audience, which drives conversation and interactions with new audiences. Whether your business needs a motion graphics designer for marketing or customer service, Dimarz can help you with excellent motion design and increase customer engagement.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\nWorking With Motions Graphic designer To Expand Your Business</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Considering motion graphics&#39; numerous advantages and value in marketing, you should hire a designer for your business. Your brand can reach new heights by working with a talented motion graphic designer who is also creative. As a motion graphics company in the industry, DiMarz offers various styles of motion design. We create visually appealing animated graphics that tell stories, promote products and give interesting visual content.</p>', 4, 'Motion Graphic Services', '<p>Motion graphics allow businesses to communicate key concepts, products, and services in an engaging and creative way. Benefits of motion graphic services include increased engagement, clarity of message, and increased memorability. Professionally created motion graphics can be used to create powerful visual stories that resonate with audiences. It can also be used to bridge language barriers and to pr