(84, 3, 10, 'Websites Speed Optimization', 'websites-speed-optimization-services', 'Boost Your Websites Speed & traffic With our Speed Optimization Services', '<h2>Importance of Websites Speed Optimization</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The first reason why website speed is so important is that it affects the user experience. If a website takes too long to load, visitors will become frustrated and likely leave the site. When a website takes more than four seconds to load, 46% of users don&#39;t return.This is especially true for mobile users, as the longer it takes for a website to load, the more likely they are to navigate away.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why businesses choose WordPress speed optimization services&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Many businesses choose to use WordPress speed optimization services to ensure their websites are running as efficiently as possible. These services use a variety of techniques to reduce the loading time of a website, including minifying code, compressing images and caching content. This can help reduce the amount of time it takes for a website to load, resulting in better customer experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Speed up your WordPress site today with DiMarz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimarz understands that your website is the face of your business, and a slow loading website can significantly hurt your sales and conversions. That&rsquo;s why we provide comprehensive optimization services to help you get the most out of your WordPress website.We look at your hosting environment, theme, plugins, and more to identify opportunities to increase the speed and performance of your website. Make your websites faster with DiMarz now!</p>', 4, 'Websites Speed Optimization Services', '<p>WordPress is a content management system (CMS) that helps you create and manage websites. WordPress Speed Optimization service is designed to help you improve your website&#39;s speed and performance. By optimizing your WordPress site, you can increase the overall efficiency of your operation and ensure that your users have a more enjoyable experience while surfing your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our WordPress Speed Optimization Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Faster loading times</li>\r\n	<li>Decent Score on Google Pagespeed Insight/GTMetrix</li>\r\n	<li>Improvement on Google Web Vitals</li>\r\n	<li>Clean/Minify unused Java scripts</li>\r\n	<li>Image Minification/ Next Gen Formatting</li>\r\n	<li>AMP integration</li>\r\n	<li>Clean Cache</li>\r\n	<li>Remove unnecessary plugins<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 84, '<h2>Why Choose Dimarz For WordPress Speed Optimization Services?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully Functional Website</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 Support System</li>\r\n	<li>Revisions</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent Communication&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 51, 84, 3, 1, '2022-12-21 18:38:27', '2022-12-21 18:38:27'),
(85, 3, 13, 'Custom Websites', 'custom-websites-services', 'Make a Custom Website According To Your Choice', '<h2>Custom Websites Convey Your Brand&#39;s Unique Value</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Your customer&rsquo;s perception of value is largely based on the way you present your brand, so having a custom website is essential.Having a custom website gives your brand a professional look and feel. It&#39;s tailored to your specifications, with the right design, layout, and features to make your website different from the competition. By working with a web designer to create a site suited to your specific needs, you can ensure that your visitors have a positive experience and understand what makes your company special.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Give Your Website a Professional Appearance</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Everyone wants a website that looks professional and polished, but doesn&rsquo;t know how to make that happen. That&#39;s where custom web design comes in. Custom web design gives you complete control over the look and feels of your site, from the colors and graphics to the layout and navigation. A professional custom website will convey high levels of professionalism, making people trust you more. This higher level of credibility will help you establish yourself as an authority in your industry.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why Partner with DiMarz for Custom Website Design Services?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to custom website design, there&#39;s no better partner than DiMarz. The DiMarz team has extensive experience in website design, development, and maintenance, allowing them to create aesthetically pleasing and highly functional websites. With our custom website design services, you&#39;ll get a stunning website optimized for conversion and fully responsive on all devices.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Custom Websites Services', '<p>Custom Website Development is a specialized service that creates a website personalized to meet a client&rsquo;s specific needs. It involves a