(88, 3, 13, 'Human Resource Management Application Development', 'human-resource-management-application-development-service', 'Manage Staffs Efficiently With Your Own HRMS Application', '<h2><br />\r\nWhat is a Human Resource Management System?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A Human Resource Management System (HRMS) is a software solution designed to help businesses manage their human capital more efficiently. It automates and streamlines the tasks associated with employee management, including onboarding, tracking, payroll, benefits, compliance, and reporting. HRMS simplifies managing employee data, making tracking information like attendance records, employee performance, and compensation packages easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Benefits of Using a Human Resource Management System</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>HRMS (Human Resource Management System) software can benefit a business. It can help in managing personnel, from recruitment and onboarding to tracking attendance and performance. This software can help managers stay organized and keep track of their employee data, Information centralization, Effective recruitment, single multifunctional solution, Efficient Collaboration, and make decisions about promotion and salary.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Choose DiMarz For Your Company HRMS&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The HRMS Services Company is the perfect choice for any business. DiMarz can assist in recruiting, staff development, and management. We are committed to providing personalized attention and customized solutions to meet an organization&#39;s needs.With DiMarz, you can complete your HR processes, decrease administrative costs, and free up valuable time for more strategic tasks<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Human Resource Management Application Development Services', '<p>Human Resource Management System (HRMS) applications are essential tools for any business. They provide a centralized platform to manage and monitor employee data, such as payroll, attendance, performance evaluation, benefits, and more. HRMS applications allow organizations to access employee records quickly, enabling them to make informed decisions quickly. We will build an HRMS Application for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our HRMS Application Development Service:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Project Management</li>\r\n	<li>Task management</li>\r\n	<li>Time Tracking</li>\r\n	<li>Milestone Tracking</li>\r\n	<li>Finances</li>\r\n	<li>Client Portal</li>\r\n	<li>Human Resource</li>\r\n	<li>Employee Management</li>\r\n	<li>Attendance Tracking</li>\r\n	<li>Leaves Management</li>\r\n	<li>Holidays</li>\r\n	<li>Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Business Software Major</li>\r\n	<li>Part</li>\r\n	<li>Balance Sheet</li>\r\n	<li>Profit and loss<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 88, '<h2>Why Choose Us</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully Functional Application</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 Support System</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent Communication&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 55, 88, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 19:04:12', '2022-12-21 19:04:12'),
(89, 3, 10, 'WordPress Bugs Fixing', 'wordpress-bugs-fixing-services', 'Fix ed Your Websites Bug & Make Smoothly Free With Our Services', '<h2>Benefits Of Bug Fixing Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As a website author, you understand the importance of keeping your website running smoothly. Unfortunately, website bug issues can lead to lost customers and revenue. WordPress bug-fixing companies can identify the source of the issue and provide you with a solution that will quickly get your website back up and running with no problem.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Best Way To Fix WordPress Bugs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a few different ways that you can go about fixing WordPress bugs. The best way to fix them is by using the built in debug feature. This will allow you to see all of the errors that are happening on your site. You can then go through and fix each one individually. Another way to fix WordPress bugs is by using a plugin or theme that has been specifically designed to fix errors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Wordpress Bug &amp; Issue we Resolved</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimarz provides technical support for WordPress users who are having issues with their website or blog. We can help with troubleshooting and fixing any bugs that may be causing problems. We also offer performance tuning, which can help to speed up your website and make it run more smoothly.Our team specializes in finding and fixing errors while keeping your website up to date with the latest WordPress versions and plugins.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Need WordPress bugs fixing quickly! Let&rsquo;s get it done</p>', 4, 'WordPress Bug Fixes Services', '<p>We provide WordPress Bugs Fixing services to keep your website running smoothly and efficiently. Our team of experienced professionals are expert in troubleshooting and fixing WordPress bugs quickly and effectively. You will get fast and reliable fixes for any WordPress issue you may encounter, such as functionality and security issues, coding errors, and plugin compatibility issues. We offer personalized support and guidance to ensure your website is free of bugs and running correctly. Our team is available to answer any questions and provide a comprehensive solution to your WordPress bug-fixing needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our WordPress Bug Fixing Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Plugin errors&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Server Error&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Clean malware Virus or Malicious code</li>\r\n	<li>Redirection Issues</li>\r\n	<li>Fix WordPress CSS issues</li>\r\n	<li>Fixing WordPress errors</li>\r\n	<li>Speed Issues Fixing</li>\r\n	<li>Elementor Issues</li>\r\n</ul>', 89, '<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Professional Bug Fixing</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 Support System</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Communication&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 60, 89, 3, 1, '2022-12-21 19:05:41', '2022-12-21 19:05:41'),
(90, 3, 13, 'POS Software Development', 'pos-software-development-services', 'Make Your Business Operations More Efficient and Cost-Friendly', '<h2>How can POS Software Help Your Businesses?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>POS software can help &nbsp;your business operations, making it easier to keep track of customer transactions and inventory. By automating certain tasks, you can free up your staff to focus on more important tasks, and increase efficiency overall. Additionally, POS software can help businesses improve their customer service by providing information about transactions and inventory status in real-time. Whether you&#39;re looking to improve your bottom line or simply make your life easier, a POS system is valuable &nbsp;for any business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A Customized Pos Development Solution For Your Business</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A customized POS solution can help your business reach its goals faster and more efficiently. It helps customers find what they&#39;re looking for, keep track of their purchases, and easier navigate the store more. When choosing a custom POS system, there are many reasons to consider, including your store&#39;s layout and size, the type of merchandise you sell, and your budget.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><br />\r\nOptimize Your Business Future with Our POS Application</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A well-functioning Point of Sale (POS) system is essential for any business. That&#39;s why we at DiMarz work hard to create the most effective POS applications for our clients. From customizing existing systems to creating completely new ones, we have the expertise and experience to help your business grow and succeed. We ensure that all of our products are fully compatible with each other so that you can maximize efficiency and performance across all areas of your business.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'POS Software Development Services', '<p>Positive aspects of using POS softwares are that they make business operations more efficient, reducing costs and time, and improving communication. Additionally, POS softwares can help to improve customer satisfaction by providing accurate information about products and services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our POS Software Development Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cloud-based POS</li>\r\n	<li>online/offline mode</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-Language system</li>\r\n	<li>Tablet supported software</li>\r\n	<li>Orders History</li>\r\n	<li>Taxes &amp; Discount feature</li>\r\n	<li>Apply coupons</li>\r\n	<li>Dashboard reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Search bar filter</li>\r\n	<li>Deals option</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth printer connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>Kitchen order receipt</li>\r\n	<li>Customer Receipt</li>\r\n	<li>Dual printer connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>Table management system</li>\r\n	<li>Pharmacy Management System,</li>\r\n	<li>Urgent Care Medication System,</li>\r\n	<li>Sales &amp; Inventory Management System,</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel Management System,</li>\r\n	<li>Lab Management System,</li>\r\n	<li>Payroll System,</li>\r\n	<li>Grade Tracking System (For Higher Institutions),</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital Management System<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 90, '<h2>Why Choose Dimarz For WordPress Speed Optimization Services?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fully Functional Application</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 Support System</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent Communication&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 54, 90, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 19:10:55', '2022-12-21 19:10:55'),
(91, 3, 11, 'React Development', 'react-development-service', 'Build Attractive Front-End With React', '<h2>React Development | Your Solution For Fast And User-Friendly Web Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>React offers businesses a fast, reliable and user-friendly solution for creating web applications. Its one-way data flow makes it easy to create dynamic, interactive user interfaces that are updated in real time. React&rsquo;s component-based architecture allows developers to create reusable code and optimize the development process. Its virtual DOM and server-side rendering capabilities also help to make applications faster and more efficient. Furthermore, its extensive library of utility functions and third-party libraries make it easier for developers to create complex applications quickly and easily. With its scalability, robustness and user-friendly features, React development is the perfect solution for businesses looking to create fast, user-friendly web applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Advantages of Developing React based Applications</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>React-based applications bring numerous benefits to users and developers. By leveraging the React library, developers can create dynamic user interfaces with minimal code, increasing efficiency, reducing development time and costs, and creating a more reliable and user-friendly experience. These features make it easier to maintain and update applications over time, reducing the time and resources it takes to keep applications up to date. Additionally, React is highly optimized for performance and loading times, ensuring a smooth and responsive user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Develop React Application With DiMarz</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our experienced developers are well-versed in the React framework and can utilize the latest technologies to develop React applications that are secure, responsive, and reliable. We are committed to providing innovative solutions tailored to meet the needs of our clients. Our team has extensive experience in building high-performance React applications that can scale easily and handle complex operations. We strive to ensure a superior user experience and maintain the highest standards of quality and reliability. With our expertise and dedication to quality, we are confident that we can deliver the best React applications in the market.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'React Development', '<p>React Development is a great way to build modern web applications. It is a JavaScript library created by Facebook and used by major companies such as Netflix, Airbnb, and Walmart. By utilizing React, developers can create user interfaces with increased flexibility and scalability. React uses a declarative syntax, making it easier to reason about the code and to debug. It is also fast, thanks to a virtual DOM which allows components to re-render efficiently when state changes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our React Development Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Complete scalable websites for personal and commercial purposes</li>\r\n	<li>API development using node js</li>\r\n	<li>Connecting frontend and backend&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>UI/UX</li>\r\n	<li>Restaurant and food application</li>\r\n	<li>Shopping application</li>\r\n	<li>Biding applications</li>\r\n	<li>Chat application</li>\r\n	<li>Progressive apps</li>\r\n	<li>Any application based on user demand<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 91, '<h2>Why Choose us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Quick and great communication.</li>\r\n	<li>Efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>Quality</li>\r\n	<li>Acceptability</li>\r\n	<li>Safety and security.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintainability<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 58, 91, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 19:52:22', '2022-12-21 19:52:22');
