(92, 3, 11, 'HTML Conversion', 'html-conversion-services', 'Convert Your Documents Into A Responsive HTML Website', '<h2>Why do you need HTML Conversion Service?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>HTML conversion services are invaluable for businesses and organizations that want to ensure their content is accessible to the widest audience. By making documents available in HTML format, users can access them on any device and in any browser. It also provides the opportunity to optimize content for better search engine visibility and improved performance. Additionally, HTML documents can be embedded into websites, providing an easy way to share content with visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Types of HTML Conversion Services We Offer</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We can provide a complete conversion service, ensuring accurate and professional results. For those who have existing HTML files that need to be converted into other formats, we offer efficient and reliable conversions to a range of formats, including PDF, XML, Word, and many more. We also offer a range of services to help clients prepare their HTML files for web publishing, including optimizing the code to ensure maximum compatibility with the majority of the browsers. By providing these comprehensive HTML conversion services, we aim to ensure that our customers have the documents they need in the format that best suits their needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Convert Any Documents to HTML with DiMarz</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our team is ready to convert any document with ease. We understand the importance of creating content that is accessible,and up-to-date with the latest web standards. Our process is thorough and we strive to ensure that all content is converted into HTML that is both user-friendly and cross-browser compatible. We use the best way and technologies available to provide the best possible results. Our team is committed to providing a high-quality conversion service. With our extensive experience and technical knowledge, we guarantee that your document will be converted into HTML with the utmost accuracy.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'HTML Conversion Services', '<p>We provide HTML Conversion services to ensure that documents, files, and content are compatible with the latest web standards. Our team of experienced professionals have extensive knowledge in the field of HTML coding and are well-versed in the latest industry trends. We will convert any of your documents accurately and efficiently.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our HTML Conversion Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Responsive and compatible with multiple devices</li>\r\n	<li>100% Hand-coded</li>\r\n	<li>W3C validated code</li>\r\n	<li>SEO friendly markup</li>\r\n	<li>Develop pages 100% like a design</li>\r\n	<li>add css3 animations and scroll animations</li>\r\n	<li>High-quality markup with proper comments<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 92, '<h2>Why Choose us:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% customer satisfaction</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited Revisions</li>\r\n	<li>Live Preview before the delivery<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 59, 92, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 19:57:47', '2022-12-21 19:57:47'),
(93, 3, 11, 'Website Bugs & Responsive Issues Fixing', 'website-bugs-responsive-issues-fixing-services', 'Make Your Website More Optimized and User-Friendly', '<h2>Optimizing Your Website Performance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A website is a great way to reach a large audience and provide a platform for selling products or services. However, ensuring that your website is optimized and free of bugs is important to provide the best user experience possible. Optimizing it will help ensure faster loading speeds, better search engine rankings, and improved visibility. Fixing bugs can also reduce potential security risks and improve user trust in your website. Additionally, customers are more likely to return to a website that is optimized and free of bugs, resulting in increased sales and revenue. Taking the time to optimize and fix bugs is an important step to ensure a successful website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Things to consider While Fixing Bugs &amp; Responsive issues on a Website</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When fixing bugs and responsive issues on a website, there are a few things to remember. First, it is essential to thoroughly test the website to identify the issues. After the problems have been identified, the next step is to troubleshoot the code and make necessary changes. Furthermore, it is crucial to ensure that these changes do not break the website&#39;s existing functionality. It will be helpful to test the website in different browsers and devices to check if the optimizations are working properly. Finally, &nbsp;document any changes made to the code for future maintenance. With these considerations in mind, we will successfully and effectively fix your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Make Your Website Fast and Responsive with DiMarz</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we understand the importance of having a website that functions properly and looks great across all devices. Our team of experienced web developers and designers will work closely with you to identify and fix any bugs or responsiveness issues that may be causing your website to malfunction. We will review your website&rsquo;s code, analyze any potential problems, and make the necessary adjustments to ensure your website is optimized for maximum efficiency. Our goal is to eliminate any issues that could be making your website difficult to navigate or appear less than stellar. With our help, you can rest assured that your website will function perfectly.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Website Bugs & Responsive Issues Fixing', '<p>Website bugs and responsive issues can be significant sources of frustration for users. Making sure websites are free of bugs and have an optimal user experience on any device requires a thorough testing process and a commitment to fixing any issues as quickly as possible. We will solve any website bugs or responsive issues for your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Website Bugs &amp; Responsive Issues Fixing Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>HTML CSS Bug Fixing</li>\r\n	<li>Fix bootstrap</li>\r\n	<li>Fix js javascript jquery</li>\r\n	<li>Fix responsiveness issues</li>\r\n	<li>Fix issues in wordpress</li>\r\n	<li>Fix layout</li>\r\n	<li>Bug fixing in your Style/Design</li>\r\n	<li>Fix any Slider/Scroller Navbar issue<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 93, '<h2>Why Choose Us:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Delivery On time</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 Support</li>\r\n	<li>100% Client Satisfaction Guaranteed<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 60, 93, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 20:03:50', '2022-12-21 20:03:50'),
(94, 3, 12, 'Laravel Development', 'laravel-development-service', 'Build Top-Notch Websites with Laravel', '<h2>Most Reliable &amp; Stable Framework With High-End Development Capability</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel is a highly reliable and stable framework that offers developers the highest level of development capability. It is built on Symfony architecture, making it a reliable and robust platform. It provides comprehensive tools and features that help developers quickly create and deploy applications. Its easy-to-use syntax makes it perfect for rapid application development, allowing developers to customize their applications easily. Furthermore, Laravel is also highly extensible, allowing developers to add custom plugins and modules as needed without compromising the application&#39;s stability.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Opportunities You Can Enjoy in Laravel-Based Framework</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With Laravel, developers can create robust, feature-rich applications. This allows for the development of powerful applications such as Learning Management Systems (LMS), Third-Party Integrations, API Development, CRM, E-Commerce websites, and more. Developers can build secure and efficient solutions by utilizing Laravel&#39;s libraries, authentication, routing, caching, and other features. Furthermore, Laravel allows developers to quickly create custom solutions, allowing them to build applications faster, with fewer bugs and more features. With the use of Laravel, businesses can rapidly create powerful applications, allowing them to quickly scale and adapt to the changing needs of their customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Build Your Laravel-Based Web Applications With DiMarz</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We will build your Laravel-based web applications to the highest standard. We are experienced in developing custom web applications and can provide necessary solutions for your business. Our team of professionals uses the latest technologies to ensure that your web application is secure and efficient and offers high