(95, 3, 12, 'PHP Development', 'php-development-service', 'Build Responsive, Featureful and User-friendly PHP Websites', '<h2>Develop Responsive &amp; Functional Web Applications With PHP</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>PHP is a powerful, versatile, open-source scripting language used to create dynamic and interactive websites. Its features offer endless opportunities for developers to create complex, secure, and efficient websites. With PHP, developers can access databases, create user-friendly interfaces, and automate tasks. It is easy to learn and implement and regularly updated to meet the ever-changing requirements of the modern web. PHP is excellent for businesses creating dynamic, secure, and feature-rich websites.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A Perfect Framework for Businesses Who Wants a Fully Customized Website</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>PHP is an open-source scripting language that is widely used for web development. It can create various web applications, ranging from interactive websites to complex web-based applications. With its help, developers can create custom content management systems, e-commerce websites, message boards, and forums. It can be used to develop dynamic web pages featuring interactive forms and user-generated content. Another good thing about PHP is the ability to create custom APIs, allowing developers to connect applications and websites to external services. Its vast library of functions and other tools make it an ideal platform for building a wide variety of web applications. We can build any kind of web application for you using PHP.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>We Provide Expert PHP Development Services for Your Business</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we provide PHP development services for businesses of all sizes. Our experienced team of developers has a proven track record of creating high-quality applications tailored to customer needs. We have an in-depth understanding of the PHP language and its many libraries. We can quickly develop custom solutions to meet any business requirement. Our developers have a wealth of experience in creating web applications, and we pride ourselves on providing the highest level of customer service. With DiMarz, you can rest assured that your development project is in professional hands.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'PHP Development Service', '<p>PHP Development is a popular web development language used to create dynamic websites and applications. It has been around since 1994 and is a widely used language for web development. PHP is open source and easy to learn, making it an ideal choice for developers of all experience levels. It is well-supported, with a large user base and community, and is constantly updated to keep up with the latest trends.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our PHP Development Services:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Web Socketing</li>\r\n	<li>Web Scraping</li>\r\n	<li>Marketing Application Development</li>\r\n	<li>Perfex CRM Customization</li>\r\n	<li>Frontend Development</li>\r\n	<li>Backend Development</li>\r\n	<li>API Development&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>API Integration&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Responsive Design</li>\r\n	<li>Database Integration</li>\r\n	<li>Laravel App Development</li>\r\n	<li>Progressive Web App</li>\r\n	<li>Realtime Chat and Notifications</li>\r\n	<li>Firebase Integration</li>\r\n	<li>FCM Integration</li>\r\n	<li>Clean Coding<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 95, '<h2>Why Choose Us:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% Satisfaction&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>No security risks&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Work&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Quality Work<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 62, 95, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 21:01:29', '2022-12-21 21:01:29'),
(96, 3, 12, 'Node.js Development', 'nodejs-development-service', 'Create Dynamic and Interactive Web Applications With Node.js', '<h2>Why Should You Go For Node.js?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Node.js is a JavaScript runtime environment that allows you to create powerful interactive web applications. It is fast and efficient and provides superior scalability and performance compared to other server-side technologies. It offers many features and advantages for building great web applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Exciting Features of Node.Js</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Node.js has revolutionized the development of web applications. It is built on the Chrome JavaScript engine and enables users to create fast, dynamic, and highly scalable web applications. It consists of various exciting features, such as its asynchronous event-driven architecture, non-blocking I/O API, and lightweight, efficient runtime environment. It also features support for many frameworks and libraries, enabling developers to create complex applications quickly. It offers a vast range of tools, such as its package manager, which makes it easy to maintain and update applications. Node.js is an ideal platform for rapidly developing web applications, allowing developers to focus on delivering value to the end user.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Node.js Services By DiMarz</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At DiMarz, we offer a range of Node.js services to meet your web development needs. Node.js is an open-source JavaScript runtime environment that enables developers to build web, desktop, and mobile applications. It is a powerful tool for creating dynamic and interactive websites and applications. Our experienced Node.js developers are well-versed in its features and capabilities, so you can rest assured that your project is in good hands. We offer various Node.js services, including creating custom web applications, developing complex web portals, creating server-side scripting, node.js application migration, and API integration. Our Node.js services cover the entire development lifecycle, from conceptualization to deployment.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 4, 'Node.js Development Service', '<p>Node.js is an open-source, cross-platform JavaScript runtime environment that provides an efficient and scalable way to build web applications. It allows developers to create dynamic and interactive web apps with a fast and intuitive programming style. Node.js is a highly efficient platform that provides developers with an array of tools and libraries to create robust and reliable applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Node.js Development Service:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Responsive design</li>\r\n	<li>Dynamic, reusable and flexible code</li>\r\n	<li>User friendly</li>\r\n	<li>Easy navigation</li>\r\n	<li>Reliable and secure</li>\r\n	<li>High-performing<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 96, '<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% Satisfaction&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>No security risks&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Work</li>\r\n	<li>Quality Work</li>\r\n</ul>', 63, 96, 5, 1, '2022-12-21 21:17:04', '2022-12-21 21:17:04');
