(6, 2, 'Website Analysis', 'We will run a deep analysis on your website to figure out the problems. We will list out the issues which are affecting your website’s performance, user experience and ranking. Then we will give you a report on the problems & recommendations associated with your website and SEO.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:08:57', NULL),
(7, 2, 'Plan SEO Strategy', 'After everything is finalized, we will create an SEO strategy checklist for your website which will include all SEO aspects; Technical, On-page, Off-Page, Keyword Research, Link Building and others. Then we will provide you with a copy of the checklist.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:09:36', NULL),
(8, 2, 'Briefing', 'We will conduct a 30-minute meeting to discuss the planning and strategy we made for your SEO campaign. After your confirmation, we will acquire the important information we need from you to get things started.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:09:50', NULL),
(9, 2, 'Reporting', 'Throughout the whole campaign, we will provide you a monthly/bi-monthly report in a PDF format informing you on the progress of your website and the changes. The report will consist of everything from top to bottom of your website including, website performance, keyword ranks, traffic, etc.', NULL, '2022-12-19 07:10:02', NULL),
(10, 3, 'CONNECT', 'When you will reach us with your requirements, we will try to connect you within a short time.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:04:59', NULL),
(11, 3, 'AGREEMENT', 'Then, we will conduct a short meeting regarding the campaign and come to an agreement. We can conduct this meeting over any meeting platforms as in; Zoom, Google Meet, Skype, etc.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:05:10', NULL),
(12, 3, 'COLLECT RESOURCE', 'Now, we will collect the resources necessary to your campaign like images, templates, server setup, etc.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:05:23', NULL),
(13, 3, 'CAMPAIGN PREPARATION & EXECUTION', 'We will implement the resources and start the campaign. In the process, we will track your campaign progress and make reports.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:05:34', NULL),
(14, 3, 'CAMPAIGN REPORT', 'After the campaign, we will provide you with an in depth statistical report on your email marketing campaign.', NULL, '2022-12-19 10:05:45', NULL),
(15, 5, 'Identifying your project requirements', 'Understanding the project\'s scope and the client\'s needs is essential. This may include specific features or a particular design or theme. We ask the client for a detailed list of their requirements so that everything is noticed.', NULL, '2022-12-19 13:53:30', NULL),
(16, 5, 'Discuss', 'We discussed the project in detail, from the design and layout to the features and plugins that would be required. We also discussed the timeline for the project and the budget, making sure that the client was happy with both.', NULL, '2022-12-19 13:54:45', NULL),
(17, 5, 'Solution analysis and review', 'We involve assessing the current and future needs of the website, as well as reviewing any existing code or themes that may already be in place. This analysis helps to identify any areas of improvement and allows us to plan the most efficient and cost-effective solution.', NULL, '2022-12-19 13:55:51', NULL),
(18, 5, 'Design & Development', 'The planning phase of a WordPress project typically involves research and analysis of the website\'s purpose, objectives, and goals. This helps to identify the features, functionality, and design elements needed to create the website. Once these factors have been identified, the design process begins. This involves creating the look and feel of the website and developing the structure and navigation.', NULL, '2022-12-19 13:56:39', NULL),
