(61, 13, 'Brainstorm your design ideas', 'Before planning to create a design, brainstorm by putting pen to paper; in design terms, brainstorming is a necessary process that involves thoughtfully designing for the client. This means coming up with ideas for creative solutions to a problem given by the client.', NULL, '2022-12-19 15:39:35', NULL),
(62, 13, 'Design', 'Now it\'s time actually to start designing. We are very careful about this section. We find the best way to translate ideas into an actual design and do what feels natural.', NULL, '2022-12-19 15:39:43', NULL),
